{"tid":1900500,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（警世）唔好食太熱嘅嘢，要等一陣先好食","createTime":"2020-02-27T09:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T09:14:49.000Z","uid":330057,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8612de4c6d4963f70f56b00c139b2d34e4c23e","tid":1900500,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"今年24歲<br />\n細細個開始已經好鍾意食啲好熱嘅嘢<br />\n覺得嗰種燙親條利嘅感覺好正<br />\n平時食公仔麵係誇張到食完碗麵嘅時候碗麵都仲有煙，飲茶嘅時候一沖完熱水就要即刻飲<br />\n燙住燙住咁樣飲<br />\n但係一年前左右開始<br />\n開始食嘢冇咩味道<br />\n同條女打茄輪都冇咩感覺<br />\n去睇醫生醫生同我講條利啲味蕓已經死晒生唔返出嚟<br />\n佢同我講咁就成世.....<br />\n所以喺度奉勸你哋食嘢真係唔好咁熱！"},{"pid":"fd0fb964ff505b3496fa00b159b4055f38ec8e08","tid":1900500,"uid":330057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點算好嚟緊嘅人生食幾好味嘅嘢都感受唔到"},{"pid":"0130cbcd49a31e0ca5e7e9d87ac5f0f470ed07c2","tid":1900500,"uid":176169,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"但你以後食幾難食既野都得啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde88312e943a97fa91db0928b3c656156707be0","tid":1900500,"uid":7587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"咁同人輸賭食屎 你贏撚硬啦"},{"pid":"c63d33ab693c381bdb5b7383d4a5b0366016f124","tid":1900500,"uid":330057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"靚嘅閪究竟係咩味道<br />\n我真係好想知道靚女啲尿係咩嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想試下啊屌"},{"pid":"898c681fc05682e1a982bb225f99eb90061a6daa","tid":1900500,"uid":100045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"你就爽啦，再臭再爛既西，你都可以大大力奶"},{"pid":"e1c0bf4874e2727cab656ebbbaaac1ac210f34c9","tid":1900500,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:18:19.000Z","msg":"痴